These googly eyes have strong adhesive backing, making them stick to most surfaces like paper, plastic, wood, or metal. They're easy to remove if needed, but hold firmly once applied. How can these googly eyes be used for crafts? They are perfect for bringing creativity to DIY projects, kids' crafts, and school activities. Stick them on cards, puppets, or homemade toys to add personality and fun to your creations. Can kids use these googly eyes easily? Absolutely! The self-adhesive design makes them easy for kids to peel and stick onto crafts. They’re great for encouraging creativity in children, and add a playful touch to any art project. What objects can I decorate with these googly eyes? You can stick these googly eyes on vases, fridges, toys, or any household items for a fun, comic effect. They’re also great for pranks, making inanimate objects appear lively and cheerful. How big are these googly eyes and how many do I get? Each pack contains 10 large 40mm googly eyes. Their size makes them ideal for creating standout craft projects or adding humour to objects around the home.
